{"id":11190,"date":"2024-03-17T16:15:09","date_gmt":"2024-03-17T09:15:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=11190"},"modified":"2024-03-17T17:24:56","modified_gmt":"2024-03-17T10:24:56","slug":"bbq-vinhome-grand-park","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/bbq-vinhome-grand-park\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u01b0\u1eddn BBQ Vinhome Grand Park"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1i Vinhomes Grand Park, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c BBQ m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng gian xanh v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b><i>Vinhomeland<\/i><\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn quy tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1eddn n\u01b0\u1edbng <\/span><b>BBQ Vinhomes Grand<\/b> <b>Park<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. \u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng gian n\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o n\u00e0y v\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng V\u01b0\u1eddn N\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu V\u01b0\u1eddn N\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ t\u1ea1i Vinhomes Grand Park:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Th\u1eddi gian ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng:<\/strong> T\u1eeb 09h00 \u0111\u1ebfn 11h00<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i:<\/strong> T\u1eeb 15h00 \u0111\u1ebfn 21h00<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/2 ti\u1ebfng (\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n giao c\u0103n h\u1ed9).<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Thanh to\u00e1n:<\/strong> Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng qua chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu V\u01b0\u1eddn N\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ t\u1ea1i Vinhomes Grand Park, qu\u00fd c\u01b0 d\u00e2n vui l\u00f2ng tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 theo c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:<\/strong> Truy c\u1eadp \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng VinID \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 thanh to\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 24 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean mang theo th\u1ebb c\u01b0 d\u00e2n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i khu V\u01b0\u1eddn N\u01b0\u1edbng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2:<\/strong> Trong app Vinhomes Ch\u1ecdn m\u1ee5c D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3:<\/strong> L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khu v\u1ef1c n\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd th\u1eddi gian<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Sau khi qu\u00fd c\u01b0 d\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd, vui l\u00f2ng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean trong khu v\u1ef1c, bao g\u1ed3m h\u1ecd t\u00ean, m\u00e3 c\u0103n h\u1ed9, s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 khi c\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4:<\/strong> Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n thanh to\u00e1n theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb th\u1ee5 h\u01b0\u1edfng:<\/strong> Chi nh\u00e1nh t\u1ea1i TP.HCM \u2013 C\u00f4ng ty C\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Vinhomes<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n:<\/strong> 19132620439074<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng:<\/strong> Techcombank \u2013 Chi nh\u00e1nh TP.HCM<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>N\u1ed9i dung thanh to\u00e1n:<\/strong> Chi ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu BBQ c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Qu\u00fd c\u01b0 d\u00e2n nh\u1edb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n thanh to\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 24 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 mang theo th\u1ebb c\u01b0 d\u00e2n khi tham gia tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i khu v\u01b0\u1eddn n\u01b0\u1edbng.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11192\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11192\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11192 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-1.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11192\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11192\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-1.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11192\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u00fd c\u01b0 d\u00e2n nh\u1edb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n thanh to\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 24 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ed9i quy V\u01b0\u1eddn n\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh chung<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khu v\u1ef1c BBQ ch\u1ec9 d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Khu \u0110\u00f4 th\u1ecb Vinhomes Grand Park.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1edbi 12 tu\u1ed5i khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu v\u1ef1c BBQ ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng than \u0111\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m trong khu v\u1ef1c BBQ.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o d\u1eadp t\u1eaft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c t\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbng sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ngay cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c c\u01b0 d\u00e2n cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 ho\u1eb7c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c m\u1ecdi t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu v\u1ef1c BBQ, do ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd b\u1ea3o h\u1ed9 g\u00e2y ra.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">H\u00e3y tu\u00e2n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Ban Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd BBQ.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u01b0 d\u00e2n t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 an to\u00e0n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb, d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 v\u00e0 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Ban Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd Vinhomes Grand Park kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_11193\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11193\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11193 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-2.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"408\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/408;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11193\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11193\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-2.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"408\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11193\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1edbi 12 tu\u1ed5i khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu v\u1ef1c BBQ ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t.<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c h\u00e0nh vi nghi\u00eam c\u1ea5m<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khu v\u1ef1c BBQ l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian chia s\u1ebb v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 quy t\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng. Xin vui l\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c, v\u0169 kh\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c h\u00e0ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c BBQ.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ma t\u00fay, ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1c, b\u00f3i to\u00e1n, m\u1ea1i d\u00e2m v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0o vi ph\u1ea1m ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m trong khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 an ninh tr\u1eadt t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng vui v\u1ebb v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Xin vui l\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y h\u01b0 h\u1ea1i, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, ho\u1eb7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 h\u00fat kh\u00f3i, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gas, x\u0103ng, d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nghi\u00eam c\u1ea5m b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, v\u1ee9t r\u00e1c b\u1eeba b\u00e3i trong khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c mang theo c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i gia s\u00fac, gia c\u1ea7m ho\u1eb7c v\u1eadt nu\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u00e0n \u00e2m thanh ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1o ra ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n sau 20h30 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 t\u0129nh l\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng xung quanh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ban Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o, l\u1eadp bi\u00ean b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00e0nh vi vi ph\u1ea1m n\u1ed9i quy. ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n vi ph\u1ea1m n\u1ed9i quy c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c BBQ \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec tr\u1eadt t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_11194\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11194\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11194 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-3.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"559\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/559;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11194\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11194\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-3.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"559\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11194\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea5m ma t\u00fay, ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1c, b\u00f3i to\u00e1n, m\u1ea1i d\u00e2m v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi h\u00e0nh vi ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt vi ph\u1ea1m trong khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">L\u01b0u \u00fd khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1ea1i Vinhomes Grand Park, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p, v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, t\u1eeb th\u1ee9c \u0103n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng. Vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb than l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m BBQ su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n v\u1ec7 sinh, tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m b\u1ea9n b\u00e3i c\u00e1t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c x\u1ea3 r\u00e1c b\u1eeba b\u00e3i.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1edbm kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn ch\u00f2i v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ebft gi\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 b\u1ed3n r\u1eeda tay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p, c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n, than v\u00e0 b\u1eadt l\u1eeda c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khu v\u1ef1c n\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u1ed5 c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec7n, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang \u0111\u1ee7 pin s\u1ea1c n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Cung c\u1ea5p xe \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ec3 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n ch\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n t\u1eeb c\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c n\u01b0\u1edbng.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u00e3y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n v\u00e0 th\u1ee9c u\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c BBQ tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi b\u00ean nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n y\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11195\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11195\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11195 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-4.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/532;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11195\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11195\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bbq-vinhomes-grand-park-4.jpg\" alt=\"bbq vinhome grand park\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11195\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khu v\u1ef1c n\u01b0\u1edbng BBQ kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u1ed5 c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec7n, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang \u0111\u1ee7 pin s\u1ea1c n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/bbq-vinhome-grand-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b> BBQ Vinhome Grand Park<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i, chia s\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. <\/span><b><i>Vinhomeland<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tin r\u1eb1ng, m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ec7c n\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 l\u00e0m gi\u00e0u th\u00eam nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 chung Vinhomes Grand Park &#8211; n\u01a1i h\u00f2a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;11190&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;0\\\/5 - (0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;C\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u01b0\u1eddn BBQ Vinhome Grand Park&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div cla